<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>About Me</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="About Me page for Your Name" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --bg-alt: #020617;
      --fg: #e5e7eb;
      --fg-muted: #9ca3af;
      --accent: #38bdf8;
      --accent-soft: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
      --border: #1f2937;
      --radius-lg: 14px;
      --radius-xl: 22px;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      --shadow-chip: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text",
        "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b 0, #020617 55%, #000 100%);
      color: var(--fg);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }

    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92));
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 28px 26px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .card {
        padding: 32px 36px 34px;
      }
    }

    .card-inner {
      display: grid;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .card-inner {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 320px) minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 32px;
      }
    }

    /* Left column */

    .profile {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .profile-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 72px;
      height: 72px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #38bdf8, #0ea5e9, #0f172a);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .avatar-badge {
      position: absolute;
      right: -2px;
      bottom: -2px;
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #22c55e, #16a34a);
      border: 2px solid #020617;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #e5fef1;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.65);
    }

    .profile-text h1 {
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .profile-text p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
    }

    .tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .tag {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 4px 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9));
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-chip);
    }

    .meta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .meta-item {
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(55, 65, 81, 0.75);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96));
    }

    .meta-label {
      color: var(--fg-muted);
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .meta-value {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .contact-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .contact-links a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 6px 11px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--fg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(156, 163, 175, 0.4);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96));
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
    }

    .contact-links a:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* Right column */

    .content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96));
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35);
    }

    .intro strong {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 700px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 12px 13px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.18), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      border: 1px solid rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.8);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .panel h2 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
    }

    .panel p {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    .panel ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
    }

    .panel li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .pill-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .pill {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(55, 65, 81, 0.9);
      color: var(--fg-muted);
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
    }

    .footer-note strong {
      color: var(--accent);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/about/">About</a>
    <article class="card" aria-label="About Me">
      <div class="card-inner">
        <!-- Left: profile summary -->
        <section class="profile" aria-label="Profile">
          <header class="profile-header">
            <div class="avatar">
              <div class="avatar-badge" title="Available for interesting work">
                •
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-text">
              <h1>Your Name</h1>
              <p>Software Engineer · Problem Solver · Builder</p>
            </div>
          </header>

          <div class="tags" aria-label="Focus areas">
            <span class="tag">Backend Engineering</span>
            <span class="tag">Developer Experience</span>
            <span class="tag">Distributed Systems</span>
            <span class="tag">Writing & Teaching</span>
          </div>

          <div class="meta" aria-label="Quick facts">
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Location</span>
              <span class="meta-value">Boise, Idaho, USA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Role</span>
              <span class="meta-value">Software Engineer</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Status</span>
              <span class="meta-value">Happily Employed</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-links" aria-label="Contact">
            <a href="mailto:you@example.com">Email</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-handle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Résumé</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Right: detailed content -->
        <section class="content" aria-label="About content">
          <section aria-label="Introduction">
            <p class="section-heading">About</p>
            <div class="intro">
              <p>
                I am a <strong>software engineer</strong> with lots of
                functional experience who enjoys designing clear systems,
                working on developer experience, and turning complex problems
                into practical business solutions. I care about maintainable
                code, building the right thing, thoughtful APIs, and tools that
                make others more effective.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="grid" aria-label="Work and interests">
            <div class="panel" aria-label="What I work on">
              <h2>What I work on</h2>
              <p>
                My professional focus is building robust services and tools that support
                real-world products. I like owning problems end-to-end, from initial
                design through implementation, testing, and long-term maintenance.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Designing and implementing backend services and APIs</li>
                <li>Improving performance, reliability, and observability</li>
                <li>Building internal tooling and developer workflows</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="pill-list">
                <span class="pill">Distributed systems</span>
                <span class="pill">Databases</span>
                <span class="pill">Testing & CI</span>
                <span class="pill">Code quality</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" aria-label="How I think">
              <h2>How I think</h2>
              <p>
                I prefer clear interfaces, boring technologies used well, and feedback
                loops that are as tight as possible. I like to document decisions,
                reason about trade-offs, and make it easy for future contributors to
                pick up where I left off.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Bias toward small, composable building blocks</li>
                <li>Measure before optimizing; automate where it pays off</li>
                <li>Write things down so they survive context switches</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="grid" aria-label="Projects and personal">
            <div class="panel" aria-label="Projects">
              <h2>Selected projects</h2>
              <p>
                Outside of work, I enjoy experimenting with tools, automation, and
                small products.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                <strong>Silo Go</strong> – File format and cli tool for packing
                and unpacking files and their contents. Like markdown for zip
                files.
                </li>
                <li>
                <strong>I wrote <a href="https://x.com/escherize/status/1948930729477644695">goto in Clojure</a></strong> – Another small highlight or experiment. https://x.com/escherize/status/1948930729477644695
                </li>
                <li>
                <strong>Writing</strong> – Articles, design docs, and technical write-ups.
                </li>
              </ul>
              <div class="pill-list">
                <span class="pill">Functional programming</span>
                <span class="pill">Tooling</span>
                <span class="pill">Open source</span>
                <span class="pill">Experiments</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" aria-label="Outside of work">
              <h2>Outside of work</h2>
              <p>
                Away from the editor, I value time with family and friends, reading,
                and learning new skills that are completely unrelated to software.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Spending time with family and close friends</li>
                <li>Teaching my kids about math</li>
                <li>Reading books on geometry, systems, and design</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          </section>
          <section aria-label="Closing">
            <p class="footer-note">
              If you would like to collaborate, talk about an idea, or just say hello,
              feel free to reach out via <strong>bryan.maass@gmail.com</strong> or connect with me on
              <strong><a href="https://x.com/escherize">twitter</a></strong>.
            </p>
          </section>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
